{%- comment -%}
  This will output a special class for differntiating between pre and post iOS7
  icons. Note that this is only applicable to iosicongallery. For the other
  sites, nothing will be output.

  ios7 release date: Sep 13 2013 (unix timestamp 1379030400)

  Includes:
    `date` - the post's data
    `classPrefix` - the class you want to add a modifier to
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign postDate = include.date | date: '%s' | plus: 0 -%}
{%- assign ios7ReleaseDate = 1379030400 -%}
{%- assign classModifier = "post-ios7" -%}
{%- if postDate < ios7ReleaseDate -%}
  {%- assign classModifier = "pre-ios7" -%}
{%- endif -%}
{% comment %}
  This is where the magic happens. We output the class prefix with the modifier
  based on the date of the icon.
{% endcomment %}
{%- if site.theeme.active == "iosicongallery" -%}
 {{ include.classPrefix }}--{{ classModifier }}
{% endif %}